data.name: Smoked Salmon and Cream Cheese Toast
data.quickTastyDescription: A delightful and easy toast topped with creamy cheese and rich smoked salmon, perfect for breakfast or a light snack!
detailedCookingInstructions: Toast the slices of whole grain bread until golden brown.
Spread 2 tablespoons of cream cheese on each slice of toasted bread.
Layer the smoked salmon evenly on top of the cream cheese.
Sprinkle capers and fresh dill over the salmon, if using.
Serve with a lemon wedge on the side for a fresh squeeze of juice.
data.detailedName: Delicious Smoked Salmon and Cream Cheese Toast
data.modifiersForBase: Topped with cream cheese and smoked salmon
